{"id":"mahazioth","term":"Mahazioth","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Visions, a Kohathite Levite, chief of the twenty-third course of musicians (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 25:4\">1 Chr. 25:4</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 25:30\">30</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 25:4","1 Chronicles 25:30"]}